            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "incident_source": [
                  "D-T"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                "The neutrons with the yield of about 1 to 3E12",
                "n/s, were produced by d-T reaction with an effective",
                "deuteron beam energy and current of 125 keV and 20",
                "mA. The thickness of the tritium-titanium (T-Ti)",
                "target was 0.9 mg/cm2."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "nuclide": "82-PB-206",
                "field_identifier": "NAT",
                "value": 0.241
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The natural lead foils of",
                "99.99% purity and 0.25 mm thickness were made into",
                "circular samples with a diameter of 20 mm. Each of",
                "them was sandwiched between natural niobium foils of",
                "the same diameter, all the niobium foils with",
                "purities better than 99.9% and 0.2 mm in thickness."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Gamma-ray activities of the residual nuclei",
                "were measured by a CH8403 coaxial HPGe detector with",
                "sensitive volume 110 cm3 and relative efficiency of",
                "20% and energy resolution of 3 keV at 1.33 MeV."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "FISCH"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Used to monitor the neutron yield fluctuation."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The Lead samples were measured after having",
                "been cooled for more than 18 times of the half-life",
                "of Pb-203g (51.873 h) to avoid the effect of the",
                "gamma-ray (279.1967 keV) from Pb-203g."
              ]
            }
